{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18d3", "eventName": "覆潮之下", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SV-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "闖入者", "storyInfo": "斯卡蒂得到線人指引，扮作流浪歌手，準備潛入鹽風城。盯上鹽風城的，除了她，還有伊比利亞的審判官。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你退步了，斯卡蒂。以前的你能輕輕鬆鬆地把他們大卸八塊。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何塞先生，我沒那麼血腥。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難說。那就是你變了。你居然還給了他們逃的機會。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能吧。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼風把你又吹到我這來了？他們在這蹲你是不是和我有關係？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說你不幹這行了，後面是加入了什麼......一個醫藥公司吧？好好的正經工作不幹，又跑來這荒郊野嶺做什麼？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何塞先生，你消息靈通。這次我需要你幫忙。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "老人舔了舔煙紙，從口袋裡拿出了些劣質煙草。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾年過去了，我還以為你收手了。因為你，卡西米爾的賞金獵人換了好幾批。這裡離卡西米爾那麼遠，我都能知道你又幹了些什麼。", "name": "老何塞"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本以為你是個只會搞大動靜的人。", "name": "老何塞"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但你現在變得這麼安靜。", "name": "老何塞"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這一路像拖車一樣從米諾斯附近碾過來，就為了找我？你想要什麼，說吧。", "name": "老何塞"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去鹽風城。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鹽......風城？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我，連你也沒聽過這地方。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我聽過。在這一帶賣消息的人裡，也只有我聽過。但你，你怎麼會想去那裡？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那地方什麼都沒了。幾十年前......就不剩下什麼了。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "靠近大海的那一大塊，你以為還能剩下什麼？不過一個空架子，呼口氣都漏風。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多賞金獵人想靠近那些荒棄的城市，就像撲向腐死馱獸骨架的小獸。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們以為還能摳出一絲能吃的血肉來，卻不知道自己吞進肚裡的不過是一包毒蟲。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊比利亞。他們覺得這個不出聲的伊比利亞也像卡西米爾和高盧一樣，到處都是寶藏。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，那裡什麼都沒有。什麼都沒有的地方就越什麼都可能有。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你會告訴賞金獵人什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們問我買消息，我會賣給他們。對我這樣的人來說，這些人回來或者回不來，都是生意。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，他們也確實回不來，一個都回不來。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半個月前，有一隊人來找我，“匕首角”的手下。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的裝備比地上這些小子要精良得多。他也很有經驗。他帶著十幾個人一起去了。現在再也沒人見過他們。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人好奇他們的下落。他們可能是被懲戒軍抓走，也可能是國防軍幹的，但我還聽說了別的可能性。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡有——怪物。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要嘛就是被審判庭抓走了。我不知道哪種下場更慘。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪物還是人，對我的劍來說區別不大。只分擋路的，和不擋路的。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，好吧。你去鹽風城，總不能是想去度假。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去找人。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又有哪個倒楣蛋惹到你了？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這回不算。那人是我的......是我以前認識的人。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......比認識我還要早？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早得多。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為他們都不在這，或者都死了。起碼你當年是這麼對我說的。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才要去找。我要弄明白一些事。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你找了也挺多年了吧？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上回那麼大動靜，不可能是為了那份騎士寶藏。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跟我說過，人該往前。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有沒有帶藏寶圖？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人，有些還是老手。他們在荒地裡走，走著走著，就忘了自己要去哪，又想找什麼。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就一直走。不知饑餓，不知疲倦。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......直到荒野將他們殺死。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們太弱了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弱？再強大的獵人，也征服不了沒有邊際的荒野。很多獵人不明不白地死在路上，到死都不知道自己要找什麼——這個結局不適合你。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要跟我說這些？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我難道沒和你說過，他們甚至都不是阿戈爾小機器的對手？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你強，你保住我兒子的命了嗎？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對不起。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要說對不起！我不是要刺你。我是要你自己想想，沒原諒你自己的是你，不是我。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我後悔的就只有沒打斷他的腿，不讓他走老子的老路。和你無關。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說自己是海裡來的，除了伊比利亞，我沒聽過其他什麼海。你是我不知道的人。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢，你就沒有不知道的人？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是那樣的人殺了我兒子。你都不知道的人。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我就是害怕那樣的事情。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罷了。至少你說的人不會費盡心思殺我。你去鹽風城做什麼？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有一個朋友被人帶去了那裡。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪事。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿好。地圖。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。我要給你什麼？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我什麼？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你賣情報。一物換一物。你給了我資訊，我給你你需要的。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（彈煙灰）", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想想......那年你把胡安那小子的屍體帶了回來，你把他交到了我手上，腦袋和胳膊還連在身體上。所以，現在我們就兩清了。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......何塞先生，非常感謝。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我走了。保重。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停！急急忙忙的，趕著去送死？！", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘿。你是不是沒怎麼聽過別人和你這麼說話？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你就需要有人這麼和你說說。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你穿一身賞金獵人的衣服，就這麼大搖大擺地進伊比利亞的城市？", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還真是老樣子啊，斯卡蒂。我費了這麼多口水，進你耳朵還不如嘩嘩的風聲。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這副模樣，國防軍能抓你十幾次！", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你準備跟他們耗多少時間？你要找的人又能等多少時間？伊比利亞人不是這些不入流的賞金獵人，沒那麼好打發。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想給我建議。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還能借你一些東西。這琴你拿著。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "琴？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會彈嗎？我記得你以前彈過。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，那更好。不會彈也沒事，你就做做樣子。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這衣服也換上。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是什麼衣服？樣子很怪。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你習不習慣不關鍵，伊比利亞人習慣。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在開始，你就是流浪歌手斯卡蒂了。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去你想去的地方吧，歌手。沿著地圖，走水路，用不上多久就能到。你的話是能的，阿戈爾人。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見了，何塞先生。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_181"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂！", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可別死在那。好歹死在認識的人旁邊。", "name": "老何塞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_181"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcoastn"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救——救命！", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這都什麼東西......纏著、纏著我不放！怎麼砍都砍不死。海邊都是這種怪物嗎？", "name": "賞金獵人"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——走開，走開啊！", "name": "賞金獵人"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道我就不該來！*卡西米爾粗口*“黃煙”那廢物，要不是當年他沒本事中了圈套，老子能淪落到來這裡撿垃圾？！", "name": "賞金獵人"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這*卡西米爾粗口*老子都快把命搭在這了！伊比利亞這鬼地方，名副其實的都是鬼！", "name": "賞金獵人"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼、什麼情況？竟然一下把這怪物削成了泥？", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......呼。不管是啥，都讓老子撿了一條命——", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——", "name": "賞金獵人"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，不能離開。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你又是誰？伊比利亞怎麼這麼多怪東西？", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二次。伊比利亞禁止傳謠。下次再開口，你需要更小心。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼啊？這打扮，這武器——", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的天，你、你是......完了，我......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，海邊清理乾淨了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡已經沒有活人了——呃，除了這個站都站不住，身上正在發出一股難聞氣味的外來者。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到什麼了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人，我什麼都沒做！我發誓，我、我只是迷路，我是不小心才進到這裡，我不是故意......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看，我這有金幣，還有別的東西，該死，很多都弄丟了......這些錢，裝備，全都給您，求您放過我吧！", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收起你的破爛。長官問問題，不是叫你說這些廢話，外來者。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "問題？什麼問題？大人，我不敢問問題......我沒有問題，我保證......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求您了，大人，我不想......不要抓我......我還不如死了算了！", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當著我的面投海？你以為自己還來得及？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這劍......我的手......差一點......嗚呃......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，清醒些了嗎？你們這些雜草爛蟲一樣的外來人，心又貪又黑，卻總是這麼容易就嚇破了膽。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......我不敢逃了，大人，我什麼都會說。", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。我不喜歡重複問問題。所以，這是最後一次。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到海邊有什麼？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我......咳咳......我看到了怪物。", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們來了幾個人？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來有十二......呃，算上嚮導，我們有十三個人。", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，他沒有撒謊。這些屍體我都在海邊找到了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你現在哭有什麼用？要不是你們闖入這裡，它們也不會找上你。違背律法的時候，就該想到代價。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，死了十二個人......這一路過來，它們的數量在變多。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們並不會離巢穴太遠。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明長官的判斷是正確的。離得越近，它們越多。那座城鎮一定有問題！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動身吧。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "name2": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這個人呢？他看到了很多不該看見的。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "饒、饒命！我能說的都說了！老爺，長官，大人......媽媽呀......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，看到什麼了？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我......", "name": "賞金獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4, "name2": "avg_npc_184", "blackstart2": 0.25, "blackend2": 0.4}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4, "name2": "avg_npc_184", "blackstart2": 0.25, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們約定過。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4, "name2": "avg_npc_184", "blackstart2": 0.25, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道這樣的行為有什麼意義。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4, "name2": "avg_npc_184", "blackstart2": 0.25, "blackend2": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你答應過的。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "答應？承諾，（軟體和骨骼的摩擦聲），諾言？之前被授予動作，之後就完成另些動作？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣要求，我回應。沒有約定，沒有承諾。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184", "blackstart": 0.25, "blackend": 0.4, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回應......當然。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊貴的使者——", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您願意回應，就已是我的榮耀。", "name": "主教"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}